ferences==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Makarova, Yelena}}\n[[Category:1973 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Russian female swimmers]]\n[[Category:Olympic swimmers of Russia]]\n[[Category:Swimmers at the 1996 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Moscow]]\n{{Russia-swimming-bio-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Lugnuts", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yelena_Makarova"}
